title: [Grawood Farmstead, Field]
description: Settled among the booths, tents, and stalls in this area of the field and under the protection of a square oilcloth umbrella sits a small cloth-draped table.  A sign made of parchment dangles from the edge of the umbrella.
paths: Obvious paths: north, east, southeast, south, west, northwest
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
